<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: rough pig union -->
  <OutlanderRoughPig.label>粗野豬聯盟</OutlanderRoughPig.label>
  <!-- EN: A loose union of hardy pigskin townships. They're willing to make friends, even with thinsnouts, but they're also ready to toss a bomb and gnaw human gristle when it suits them. Treat them with respect and they'll offer a trotter to an ally in need. Turn against them and the last thing you hear might be a triumphant battle squeal. -->
  <OutlanderRoughPig.description>粗勇的豬皮人組成的鬆散城鎮。他們願意交朋友，甚至是和薄鼻子們，但是他們隨時準備丟出炸藥和咬下人類的鼻軟骨幫你整形。互相尊重他們就會對需要援助的盟友伸出蹄手。背叛他們的話那你生前最後會聽到的就會是一聲嘶叫戰吼了。</OutlanderRoughPig.description>
  <!-- EN: prime councilor -->
  <OutlanderRoughPig.leaderTitle>議長</OutlanderRoughPig.leaderTitle>
  <!-- EN: pig -->
  <OutlanderRoughPig.pawnSingular>豬頭</OutlanderRoughPig.pawnSingular>
  <!-- EN: pigs -->
  <OutlanderRoughPig.pawnsPlural>豬頭</OutlanderRoughPig.pawnsPlural>
  
  <!-- EN: waster pirates -->
  <PirateWaster.label>荒地人海賊</PirateWaster.label>
  <!-- EN: A loose collection of violent pirate bands made up primarily of wasters - xenohumans engineered to thrive around toxins and pollution. They have little interest in building, or farming, preferring to take their sustenance from others using violence.\n\nTheir technology level depends mostly on who they've managed to steal from recently. Mostly they carry gunpowder weapons, though some prefer to stab victims at close range. -->
  <PirateWaster.description>暴力的海賊團隊組成的鬆散集團，大多是荒地人 - 被改造成能夠在毒素和污染中壯大的異種人。他們對建築或耕種沒有什麼興趣，他們更喜歡使用暴力從他人那裡獲取食物。\n\n他們的科技水平主要取決於他們最近從誰那裡偷了東西。他們大多攜帶火藥武器，雖然有些人更喜歡近距離突刺。</PirateWaster.description>
  <!-- EN: boss -->
  <PirateWaster.leaderTitle>頭目</PirateWaster.leaderTitle>
  <!-- EN: waster -->
  <PirateWaster.pawnSingular>荒地人</PirateWaster.pawnSingular>
  <!-- EN: wasters -->
  <PirateWaster.pawnsPlural>荒地人</PirateWaster.pawnsPlural>
  
  <!-- EN: yttakin pirates -->
  <PirateYttakin.label>依達人海賊</PirateYttakin.label>
  <!-- EN: A close-knit band of hulking, fur-bodied pirates of the yttakin xenotype. They refuse to deal with outsiders and are quick to call their animal warriors against those who disrespect them - or whose wealth they intend to take.\n\nOriginally engineered to populate the icy planet Yttak, yttakin now pursue their traditional lifestyle on many worlds. -->
  <PirateYttakin.description>一群團結的依達人海賊，擁有壯碩且毛茸茸的身體。他們不願與外人交流。他們能快速召喚動物戰士來對付任何威脅他們或不尊重他們的人 - 或是被他們盯上的有錢人。\n\n他們最初被改造用於居住在冰冷的依達星球上，現在依達人在許多世界追求他們傳統的生活方式。</PirateYttakin.description>
  <!-- EN: boss -->
  <PirateYttakin.leaderTitle>頭目</PirateYttakin.leaderTitle>
  <!-- EN: yttakin -->
  <PirateYttakin.pawnSingular>依達人</PirateYttakin.pawnSingular>
  <!-- EN: yttakin -->
  <PirateYttakin.pawnsPlural>依達人</PirateYttakin.pawnsPlural>
  
